extendedInfo.description: Spring is the jumping platformer that takes it to the next level!- Pick up colored flowers for power-ups. Complete a 'chain' of flowers for stronger power-ups!- Play with two different characters, with their own unique attacks and power-ups.- Battle many different enemies.The free version contains the first 8 levels. You can buy the full version to get two more worlds, more enemies and an endless Arcade Mode.

reviews.comment: Wariacja na temat doodle jump - da sie pograc, jesli autor dopracuje kilka elementow moze byc fajne. Brakuje glownie muzyki i dzwiekow.
